sequenceDiagram
  actor TEC as Tecnico
  participant APP as CapturaPage
  participant SCANNER as WifiScanner
  participant CUBIT as CapturaCubit
  participant BACKEND as Backend /mediciones
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  TEC->>APP: tocar punto en plano
  APP->>SCANNER: iniciar escaneo
  SCANNER-->>APP: resultados WiFi
  APP->>CUBIT: enviar lote
  CUBIT->>BACKEND: POST /api/mediciones
  BACKEND->>DB: insertar punto y mediciones
  DB-->>BACKEND: ids y nivel
  BACKEND-->>CUBIT: 201 Created
  CUBIT-->>APP: actualizar plano
  APP-->>TEC: mostrar badge por nivel
